fulltitle: Charles McPherson Interview by Monk Rowe - 2/12/1998 - San Diego, CA
title: Charles McPherson Interview by Monk Rowe - 2/12/1998 - San Diego, CA
description:
Alto saxophonist Charles McPherson speaks about his composing process, developing an individual sound, working with Charles Mingus, and the nature of the creative arts.
